    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, a small dent on the rear passenger panel, and some light scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear on the driver's seat and some minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a set of tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been maintained regularly but definitely reflects its mileage and age.",
