    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the power band. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile gear engagement, paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior lateral traction. The chassis has been enhanced with preventative rear subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings for precise handling. A mechanically robust driver's car that balances raw performance with legendary BMW engineering.",
