    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a careful walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014standard signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the charcoal leather seats are supple and free of cracks or stains, and the dual-zone climate control blows ice-cold. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium 12-speaker sound system, is in full working order. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It features a complete service log, with the most recent full synthetic oil change and filter replacement completed just 500 miles ago. The transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with roughly 75% tread life remaining. This has been a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle, garaged nightly to preserve its condition. It is a reliable, turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
